data.description: *VA assumable loan for VA buyers*   Welcome to this reimagined rambler on a beautifully landscaped lot in the heart of Alexandria City.    Highlights of the main level include an open floor plan with hardwood floors, light-filled living room, delightful dining room, gorgeous gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite counters, and tile backsplash;  inviting primary bedroom, second bedroom, newly renovated full bathroom, powder room and bonus/three season room.  The spacious walk-out lower level includes a large rec room, two bedrooms, and a full bathroom.  The fully fenced backyard is perfect for winter nights by the fire pit and summer barbecues on the lawn.   The large cedar shed provides plenty of room for tools, gardening items, bikes, and more.   The large driveway accommodates 4 cars with an additional parking space behind the front gate. The home is ideally located within a short stroll to shopping, dining, schools and parks, and commuting is a dream - 7 miles to DC,  6 miles to Reagan National Airport, 3 miles to Old Town. This home is truly move-in ready!
